terms.medium_def:
A man from the tribe of Judah living before Israel's Monarchy, only mentioned at 1Ch.4.13; 
only referred to as Hathath (חֲתַת); 
son of Othniel whose wife was Achsah; 
a brother of Meonothai(?). § son of Othniel and grandson of Kenaz, the brother of Caleb

A man from the tribe of Judah living at the time of Divided Monarchy, only mentioned at 1Ch.4.16; 
only referred to as Tiria (תִּירְיָא); 
son of Jehallelel; 
a brother of Ziph, Ziphah and Asarel. § a Judaite, son of Jehaleleel
